Baadhitaanka hiddaha ayaa muujinaya in coronavirus-ka ay ku jiraan hiddo-wadaha ka soo jeeda jiilka betacoronavirus, jiilka hoose ee serbevirus (lineage B) iyo laba nooc oo ka yimid noocyada kale ee 'Litt Waff'.
Heer kasta oo hidde ah, shaybaarka coronavirus-ka kale ee shimbirta (BatCov RaTG13) wuxuu u eg yahay 96% noocyada kale.
Bishii Febraayo 2020, cilmi baarayaasha Shiinaha waxay ogaadeen in farqiga u dhexeeya noocyada qaarkood ee hiddo-wadayaasha pandemics iyo fayraska aadanaha uu yahay hal amino acid oo keliya.
Isbarbardhiga guud ee hidde-wadaha ayaa ilaa hadda lagu ogaaday in qiyaastii 92% walxaha hidde-wadaha ay wadaagaan coronavirus-ka pangolin iyo SARS-CoV-2, taas oo ku filan in la xaqiijiyo in pangolins ay yihiin kuwa dhexdhexaadka ah.
Cudurka fayraska waxaa lagu daaweyn karaa iyadoo la eegayo astaamaha, laakiin waxaa lagu xaqiijin karaa falcelinta silsiladda polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) ama sawirada CT.
Daraasad lagu sameeyay Wuhan oo isbarbar dhig ku sameysay PCR iyo CT ayaa muujisay in CT ay ka nugul tahay PCR, laakiin waxay muujineysaa aragti yar oo la mid ah kansarka sanbabada iyo hababka kale ee cudurka.
Laga bilaabo Maarso 2020, American College of Radiology waxay ku talineysaa CT in aan loo isticmaalin baaritaanka COVID-19 ama tijaabada safka koowaad.
Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka ayaa soo saaray daabacaaddii ugu horreysay ee 17kii Janaayo ee 2021 tilmaamaha baaritaanka RNA ee loogu talagalay daraasadda SARS-CoV-2.
Tijaabada ayaa isticmaaleysa falcelinta silsiladda polymerase-reverse-reaction (rRT-PCR) ee waqtiga dhabta ah.
