Dhamaadkii 1990-meeyadii iyo bilowgii qarnigii 21aad, beddelaadda nadaafadda gacmaha ee aan khamriga iyo biyaha la isticmaalin (oo loo yaqaan gacmo nadiifiyeyaasha aan khamriga la isticmaalin, gacmo nadiifiyeyaasha antiseptic, ama nadiifiyeyaasha gacmaha) ayaa noqday mid caan ah.
Inta badan waxaa loo sameeyay si loo yareeyo saameynta ay ku yeelan karto maaddada dufanka leh sida carbomer (polymer of ocularic acid) gel, ama dareeraha glycerin, ama boodhka, iyo isticmaalka qalajinta aalkolada.
Ku darista hydrogen peroxide oo isku dhafan ayaa kordhisa waxqabadka bakteeriyada ka baxsan. Nadiifiyeyaasha gacmaha ee ay ku jiraan ugu yaraan 60 ilaa 95% aalkolo ayaa ah kuwa waxtarka leh ee jeermiska.
Qalabka lagu nadiifiyo khamriga wuxuu dilaa bakteeriyada, bakteeriyada daawooyinka u adkaysta (MRSA iyo VRE), bakteeriyada sanbabada, fayrasyada qaarkood (HIV, herpes, RSV, rhinovirus, tallaalka, hargabka iyo hepatitis) iyo fangaska.
