Nadiifiyeyaasha gacmaha ee khamriga ku jira si buuxda uma shaqeeyaan ka saarista fayraska cudurka mindhicirka (ama norwecke), oo sida caadiga ah keena cudurka mindhicirka ee ugu faafa. Nadiifiyeyaasha gacmaha ama nadiifinta khamriga waa in loo isticmaalaa si loo qalajiyo ama loo daboolo labada gacmood.
