b'Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) waa enzyme ku jira unugyada wadnaha, xididdada dhiigga, wadnaha, kelyaha iyo mindhicirka.
ACE2 waxay ka dhigeysaa bartilmaameed daawo oo rajo leh daaweynta cudurrada xididdada dhiigga iyadoo la yareynayo heerarka angostin-II iyo kordhinta Ang (1-7) iyadoo la hor istaagayo dhaqdhaqaaqa enzyme-ka angotensin-transducer (ACE). ACE2 waxay u adeegtaa barta gelitaanka unugyada qaar ka mid ah coronavirus-ka.
Enzyme-ka aadanaha waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Angrostin-enzyme 2 waa zinc-ka ku jira ironloenzyme oo laga helo dusha sare ee unugyada endothelial iyo unugyada kale.
Borotiinka ACE2 waxaa loo qoondeeyay domain N-terminal peptidase M2 iyo domain C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transducer.
ACE2 waa nooc I oo ah nooc ka mid ah noocyada infekshanka, taas oo ah enzyme-ka ugu firfircoon ee ku jira sambabada iyo xubnaha kale ee jirka.
ACE2 waxaa laga soo saaraa unugyada gudaha unugyada oo ay ka soo saarto enzyme kale oo la yiraahdo Shidas, natiijada waxaa loo sii daayaa wareegga dhiigga sida borotiin la milmi karo, ugu dambeyntiina waxaa loo sii daayaa kaadida.
ACE2 waxaa laga helaa qaybaha badankood ee jirka: ACE2 waxay ku xidhan tahay inta badan unugyada unugyada alveolar ee nooca II ee sambabada, unugyada mindhicirka yar, unugyada xididdada dhiigga iyo unugyada xididdada dhiigga iyo unugyada unugyada muruqyada jilicsan ee unugyada jirka.
Muujinta ACE2 mRNA waxay ku jirtaa qanjirka maskaxda, stratum, hypothalamus iyo unugyada maskaxda.
Shaqada ugu weyn ee ACE2 waa in ay noqoto dheelitirka ACE.
ACE waxay u gudubtaa hormoonka angiotensin I oo u gudubta angiotensin II oo xannibaya xididdada dhiigga.
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale ku kala gooysaa amino acid-ka carboxyl terminal ee phenyllalanine oo ka yimaada angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) oo ay biyo gelisaa si ay u noqoto angiostatin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH) oo ah vasodilator.
ACE2 waxay burburin kartaa dhowr peptides oo ay ka mid yihiin [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, iyo ghrelin.
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale xakameysaa xarkaha SLC6A19, oo ah isugeynta amino acid dhexdhexaad ah, waxaana la ogaaday inay ku lug leedahay cudurka wadnaha.
Sida borotiinka transmembrane, ACE2 wuxuu u adeegaa sida barta ugu weyn ee lagu galo unugyada qaar ka mid ah fayraska corona, oo ay ku jiraan HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (fayraska keena SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (fayraska keena COVID-19).
Gaar ahaan, borotiinnada S1 ee SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV2 waxay ku xiran yihiin unugyada domain ee enzymes ACE2 si ay u fududeeyaan fayraska iyo enzymes-ka inay galaan iyo wareegaan endosomes-ka unugyada.
