Daawooyinka ka hortagga fayraska ee dib loo isticmaalay ayaa intooda badan laga soo saaray cilmi baaris Shiinees ah, iyadoo la soo sheegay in sagaal tijaabo oo cutubka III ah oo lagu sameeyay dhowr dal dhammaadkii Abriil.
Ilaa Abriil 2020, qiimeyn firfircoon ayaa la sameeyay horumarka caafimaad ee tallaalka COVID-19 iyo daawooyinka musharaxiinta. Reflovir, chloroquine iyo hydrochloroquine, lopevia / rutanavir, iyo lopenavir / rudonavir oo ay weheliso interferon beta, daawooyin badan oo ka hortagga fayraska ayaa dib loo eegayaa daaweynta COVID-19.
Waxaa jira cadeymo la taaban karo oo ku saabsan waxtarka qiimo dhimista illaa Maarso 2020.
Isticmaalka naxariista ayaa lagu muujiyay horumar caafimaad oo ku yimid bukaanada.
Tijaabooyinka caafimaad ee heerka III ayaa ka socda Mareykanka, Shiinaha iyo Talyaaniga. Chloroquine, oo hore loogu isticmaalay daaweynta duumada, ayaa markii ugu horreysay lagu bartay Shiinaha bishii Febraayo 2020.
